lead_paragraph: Tom Brady has four Super Bowl rings, is a future Hall of Famer and his New England Patriots are off to a 4-0 start, yet he's still quick to mention his 199th rank in the draft more than a decade ago as motivation for excellence.

headline.main: Tom Brady on Deflategate, Gisele and Trump
